{"id":49,"title":"*问：**什么是数据结构？有哪几种常见的数据结构？各自有什么特点？","slug":"*问：**什么是数据结构？有哪几种常见的数据结构？各自有什么特点？-1766595048","excerpt":"","content":"**参考回答：**数据结构是指计算机中组织和存储数据的方式，体现数据元素之间的特定关系。常见的数据结构包括数组、链表、栈、队列、树、图、堆、哈希表等，每种都有不同特点：数组支持随机访问但增删效率低；链表适合频繁插入删除但查找需要遍历；栈是后进先出（LIFO）结构，常用于函数调用管理；队列是先进先出（FIFO）结构，常用于任务调度；树具有分层关系便于快速查找和排序；图可表示复杂网络关系；堆是一种完全二叉树，可高效地获取最大或最小值；哈希表通过散列函数提供近似常数时间的查找和插入。\n\n","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"PUBLIC","status":"PUBLISHED","published_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:48.975921+08:00","last_edited_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:48.975921+08:00","notion_page_id":"1f95d23c-2eec-807e-8ed3-e5544423e0e7","notion_last_edit":"2025-05-20T05:56:00Z","author_id":1,"author":{"id":1,"username":"admin","email":"admin@example.com","role":"ADMIN","is_verified":true,"is_active":true,"avatar":"","bio":"","last_login_at":"2025-12-20T00:47:21.462367+08:00","email_verified_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:23.810219+08:00","created_at":"2025-12-19T09:00:38.872854652Z","updated_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:24.010602+08:00","is_admin":true},"stats":{"id":49,"blog_post_id":49,"blog_post":{"id":0,"title":"","slug":"","excerpt":"","content":"","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"","status":"","author_id":0,"author":{"id":0,"username":"","email":"","role":"","is_verified":false,"is_active":false,"avatar":"","bio":"","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","is_admin":false},"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},"view_count":0,"like_count":0,"share_count":0,"comment_count":0,"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.604909+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.604909+08:00"},"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:48.975921+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:48.975921+08:00"}